{"tid":420052,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"弊！卡華積心臟病無限期休戰","createTime":"2017-10-01T05:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T07:07:02.000Z","uid":91152,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dad5383e681e96b7bd33eb37dd7382e5bdefc161","tid":420052,"uid":91152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:21:52.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=124MPmTb5GpcFqLGG2F%2FZDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=512831d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里於周六宣佈，右閘丹尼爾卡華積因為心臟問題，暫時無限期休戰。<br />\n<br />\n丹尼爾卡華積（Dani Carvajal）今季踢足皇家馬德里所有比賽的每1分鐘，是右閘頭號人選，但現在因為其心臟問題，需要長時間治療才能痊癒，所以在健康為上的大前題下，將會全面休戰，有指他至少要養病1個半月。<br />\n<br />\n由於皇馬已有兩名左閘馬些路及迪奧靴南迪斯養傷，如今丹尼爾卡華積又要養病，因此在周日西甲主場迎戰愛斯賓奴一役，中堅拿祖費南迪斯將會串演左閘，而小將阿舒拉夫則會擔任右閘。除了缺陣皇馬的比賽之外，丹尼爾卡華積也將缺陣西班牙即將舉行的兩場國際賽。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的丹尼爾卡華積出生自皇馬青訓，於2012年加盟利華古遜，因為表現出色而在1季後被回購，立即成為正選右閘。"},{"pid":"c163b79893ac47f91f36327cfae960ffebd39f97","tid":420052,"uid":1977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:23:06.000Z","msg":"azp可以擔正國家隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12ca7b5577eeba71471be524bac7f9bbfa7ad2f","tid":420052,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:26:20.000Z","msg":"跑撚到心臟病啦場場咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"970bd2c583950b3cf62b3a85b2fde8573f60613c","tid":420052,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"皇馬又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80de89677e0f88cf583b9ad0b8b77a67dbb5a68b","tid":420052,"uid":124667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T06:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主"},{"pid":"48e711c96c742429dbe18f3dbb29eaa504b9d1ad","tid":